4For Loop{
   code soo lalabalahay in hal mar qprno        amh shaqooyinka soo lablato har loo dhibaaa 

  a) for loop                  // waxa loistimaalaa shqooyi aad oktahay in oo soo lalapanaayo

           qacido for loop
   for (initialization; condition; increment) {
    // code to be executed


    b)Meaningful Example: 
          
          const students = ["Alice", "Bob", "Charlie"];
           for (let i = 0; i < students.length; i++) {
          console.log("Hello, " + students[i] + "!");
         }
         // Output: Hello, Alice!, Hello, Bob!, Hello, Charlie!


    c) While Loop

}

